item.title: S60E10 Love is gratitude
item.description: Thank you for listening, thank you for walking with me, dear friends. Postie Nige chimes in with a voicenote announcing Christmas, and I commit to some seasonal episodes for members of the Walk the Pod lunchtime walk club. See you in 2026! Join the Walk the Pod Lunchtime walk club for weekly walking challenges, theme voting, private Discord server, photos, postcards, and stickers! https://www.patreon.com/c/rachelwheeley Feed: https://feed.podbean.com/walkthepod/feed.xml
